-30/201906301561898567.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">5.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/85239/">林肯大战僵尸</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%B0%8F%E6%AF%94%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E5%A5%A5%E4%BC%AF%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9------------/" target="_blank">小比尔·奥伯斯特</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%85%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E8%B5%AB%E6%B4%9B%E6%B3%BD------------/" target="_blank">克里斯·赫洛泽</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Jason------------/" target="_blank">Jason</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Vail------------/" target="_blank">Vail</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E7%90%86%E6%9F%A5%E5%BE%B7%C2%B7%E6%B2%99%E5%9B%A0%E5%85%8B%E6%9B%BC--------/" target="_blank">理查德·沙因克曼</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/10/" target="_blank">恐怖片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2012/" target="_blank">2012</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>19世纪，经历了影响深远的南北战争，美国终于迎来了新的时代亚伯拉罕·林肯（比尔·奥伯斯特 Bill Oberst, JR 饰）接连取得与人类的胜利，却不得不面对新的敌人。他麾下一直部队在巡察途中遭遇活死人，三十人仅有一人幸存，但由于惊吓过度精神失常。北方政府怀疑这是南方的最新武器，于是计划派出一支1</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/85239/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/84965/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-06-25/201906251561441485.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">3.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/84965/">新村僵尸漫画</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%9C%B4%E5%9F%BA%E9%9B%84------------/" target="_blank">朴基雄</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%8D%97%E5%A5%8E%E4%B8%BD------------/" target="_blank">南奎丽</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%BA------------/" target="_blank">李大为</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%9F%B3%E6%98%87%E5%AE%8C--------/" target="_blank">柳昇完</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----%E9%87%91%E6%B3%B0%E5%8B%87--------/" target="_blank">金泰勇</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----%E9%9F%A9%E5%BF%97%E6%89%BF--------/" target="_blank">韩志承</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/10/" target="_blank">恐怖片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">韩国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2014/" target="_blank">2014</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>电影《新村僵尸漫画》由柳承莞、韩智胜及金泰勇三位导演共同执导，KAFA FILMS出品在未来社会，丧尸们和人类和平共处，并作为体力劳动者一边接受治疗一边生活，而人类和丧尸之间也产生了爱情。 《新村丧尸漫画》以新村、丧尸和漫画为素材，是一部包含着动作、爱情、剧情的电影，有3位导演执导3个短片结合而成。</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/84965/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/84171/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-06-16/201906161560655789.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">7.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">12集全/已完结</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/84171/">僵尸世界2018</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-----------/" target="_blank">日本</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span clas